      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good shape and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. It\u2019s a clean, solid car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, showing only the minor, expected wear of a well-loved daily driver. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that balances quality and value, this is the one for you!",
