    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and light scratches consistent with normal use. The interior is in great shape with no tears in the fabric, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
