    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or hitting the road for a weekend getaway, this car is ready to go! It runs smoothly, looks great, and is just waiting for its next adventure. I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
