      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Power is managed through a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to its M-division tuning, offering sharp turn-in and balanced lateral grip. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing that signature 8,000 RPM crescendo. A mechanically sound, driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
